data.description: This delightful 4 bedroom, 2 bath home is nestled on a lovely lot and is just waiting for you to add your own splash of character to the already charming interior. Enjoy a Saturday morning at the local Farmers Market and then come home to whip up some fresh fare in your functional kitchen. Beautiful LVP floors adorn throughout the home, while new carpet in the bedrooms add a fresh and updated feel to the space. This home is ready and waiting for your signature style.
